  "body": "**Component**\r\nForge\r\n\r\n**Have you ensured that all of these are up to date?**\r\n :ballot_box_with_check: Foundry\r\n :ballot_box_with_check: Foundryup\r\n\r\n**What version of Foundry are you on?**\r\nforge 0.2.0 (d896050 2022-10-20T15:10:25.6227974Z)\r\n\r\n**What command(s) is the bug in?**\r\nforge script --ledger\r\n\r\n**Operating System**\r\nWindows 11 Professionnel 22H2\r\n\r\n**Describe the bug**\r\n\r\ni'm using the following command : \r\n\r\n`forge script script/DeployToMumbai.s.sol:DeployToMumbaiScript --ledger --hd-paths \"m/44'/60'/0'/0\" --rpc-url $ALCHEMY_MUMBAI_RPC_URL --broadcast -vvvv`\r\n\r\nand get this error : \r\n\r\n> Error:\r\n> **Ledger device not available.**\r\n> \r\n> Context:\r\n> - Response too short. Expected at least 2 bytes. Got []\r\n\r\nMy ledger is seen by my computer.\r\n\r\n> Ethereum App: 1.9.20\r\n> Blind singing: Enabled\r\n\r\n",
