    "body": "In case it helps, got ledger working for `forge script` with\r\n```\r\nforge script script/DeployScript.s.sol --rpc-url $RPC_URL \\\r\n--ledger --sender 0x<HW_WALLET_ADDRESS_0> \\\r\n--broadcast\r\n```\r\n\r\nThis will use the 0-indexed address from your wallet - make sure the `--sender` value matches",
